Isang lubos na pasasalamat para sa ating mga frontliners. Para sa amin, #KayoAngBituin. ✨
(Written by Carlo Hornilla for @met_tathione)
.
.
"Bituin"
Pag-ibig ang pananatiling paglilingkod nang tapat
Sa pagsapit ng dilim na kaylalim
at kaylawak
Ang nagsisilbing pag-asa ay ang liwanag ninyong hawak.
Tila ang bawat isa’y mga talang,
hindi man namin tuluyang mahawakan at mayakap,
Natatanaw namin ang inyong pagkislap.
Panalangin naming hindi kayo mapundi.
Hinihintay namin ang inyong pag-uwi.
kayo ang payong na hindi tumitiklop.
Kayo ang sinasandalang dingding.
Kayo ang bubong na kumukupkop.
Kayong piniling mawalay sa mga mahal sa buhay.
Nais naming sumaludo. Nais naming pumalakpak.
Kayong mga nag-aalay ng buhay,
Kayo ang aming mga bituin.

node.text:
December 10, 2019. ABS-CBN Christmas Special. Another truly unforgettable night for me and DJ. ❤

I decided to share this video in honor of our fans who have been with us from the very beginning. Alam namin na hindi madali yung pinagdadaanan niyo para lang masuportahan kami. This video is just a snippet of your hard work and sacrifices, and I know it doesn't give justice to the credit you rightfully deserve but still we want you to know this: We see you, we feel you, and we appreciate you. Behind the success of every celebrity is a dedicated fandom—and whatever success we have today, we owe it all to you.

To our KathCakes, Solid DJPs, and KathNiels, seeing all of you united makes us so happy. DJ and I couldn't be prouder to tell the world that we belong to these fandoms. Thank you for showering us with your love and energy as we performed on stage. It's our 9th Christmas special together pero hindi pa rin kayo napapagod, and every year keeps on getting better. Salamat dahil andyan pa din kayong lahat. DJ and I are proud to have fandoms that treat each other like family, protect each other at all cost, and make all the impossible possible. You are more than what we deserve and what we could ever ask for. Maraming salamat sa inyong lahat! Mahal namin kayo. 💙

#kathniels
#solidDJP
#kathcakes
Edited by @kevinmartelino
🎥 by @dianazoned
